		<final id="MESSAGES_02_FINALWAVE"> <![CDATA[Final Wave!]]> </final>
		<nightmare id="MESSAGES_03_NIGHTMARE"> <![CDATA[Survive!]]> </nightmare>
		
		<lose id="MESSAGES_03_LOSE"> <![CDATA[Oh no! They're taking over the ship.<br />Hey! Watch the hair.]]> </lose>
		
		<win id="MESSAGES_04_WIN_1" level="1"> <![CDATA[Whew, great job!<br />Let's get out of here while we still can!]]> </win>
		<win id="MESSAGES_04_WIN_2" level="2"> <![CDATA[Wow, you just rocked those guys!<br />We should hit the sky before more show up!]]> </win>
		<win id="MESSAGES_04_WIN_3" level="3"> <![CDATA[Ha, looks like I showed them who's boss!<br />You helped too.]]> </win>
		<win id="MESSAGES_04_WIN_4" level="4"> <![CDATA[Fantastic work!<br />You have clearly seen me do this before.]]> </win>
		<win id="MESSAGES_04_WIN_5" level="5"> <![CDATA[Nice work back there!<br />Let's get back to the Dreadyacht and get out of here.]]> </win>
		<win id="MESSAGES_04_WIN_6" level="6"> <![CDATA[Boom! We did it!<br />Looks like it's smooth sailing from here, Thanks!]]> </win>
		
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_01" step="1"> <![CDATA[Looks like we might need to set down here for a bit,<br />better set up some defenses!]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_02" step="2"> <![CDATA[We'll need some money before we do anything,<br />let's place a Treasure Chest down.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_03" step="3"> <![CDATA[Tap this square to place it down!]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_04" step="4"> <![CDATA[Great Job! Now we can collect the coins the chest makes.<br />Smart crew, you must take after me.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_05" step="5"> <![CDATA[Coins will also fall from the sky. Tap the Coin to Collect It!<br />Hey, flying ships don't exactly pay for themselves.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_06" step="6"> <![CDATA[Keep Collecting Coins!<br />You need them to buy items and Skylanders.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_07" step="7"> <![CDATA[That's enough to ask a Skylander for help.<br />Select Trigger Happy!]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_08" step="8"> <![CDATA[Now place that little guy over here!]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_09" step="9"> <![CDATA[Ah! That Chompy can really mess up my ship!<br />You'd better stop it!]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_10" step="10"> <![CDATA[Thanks!<br />I'm glad I could inspire you with my signature rugged calm.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_11" step="11"> <![CDATA[That was good, but I think we can do better.<br />Let's take him back.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_12" step="12"> <![CDATA[I bet he would be even more powerful on his elemental symbol.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_13" step="13"> <![CDATA[Select a tech-type Skylander like Trigger Happy.<br />Use the money the chest has made; I'll pay you back later.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_14" step="14"> <![CDATA[Now put him on this elemental tile.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_15" step="15"> <![CDATA[Looks like there's some more.<br />I'd get it but it looks like you're in a groove.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_16" step="16"> <![CDATA[Whoa!<br />Who ordered the Chompies well done?]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_17" step="17"> <![CDATA[More?! I don't know if we're gonna get through this time!<br />Try the Anvil Rain item!]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_18" step="18"> <![CDATA[This item calls down anvils from the sky, damaging every enemy.<br />I hope I can buff these dents out of the ship later.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_19" step="19"> <![CDATA[Ha, looks like we taught them a lesson!<br />I always had complete faith in you.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_20" step="20"> <![CDATA[Remember, you can use the items over here any time you need them.]]> </tutorialMessage>
		<tutorialMessage id="MESSGAES_TUTORIAL_21" step="21"> <![CDATA[I'd show you some of my moves but we should get back on the road.<br />Er, sky -- You know what I mean.]]> </tutorialMessage>
	</messages>
